data.value:
Welcome to ModNote!
This program allows you to keep track of your modules and take notes for each one. You may Add/Amend/Delete modules as you like.
All the module information is displayed in the modules tab while the assessments information is displayed on the assessments tab.
The notes tab allows you to create or view notes for specific modules by saving each note into a folder of the module that you have selected.
